free formula comes in a glass pot with a brush built into the cap. While the brush isn't the most amazing quality (you'll want to use a regular size brow brush), it's handy if you're in a pinch.", "Perhaps one of the most convenient feature of Ka-Brow is just how easy it is to work with. We found ourselves taking less time than normal to fill in our brows\u2014a welcome change\u2014and it held up through a standard workday, no touch-ups required. Ka-Brow offers versatility whether you're going for statement brows or those that blend in a softer way. Nice work, Benefit!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 36}
