{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/ultimate-brows-shade-shaper-pencil/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyebrow-pencil-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyebrow-pencil-reviews ", "product_names": "Ultimate Brows Shade & Shaper Pencil", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyebrow Makeup", "brand": "Ulta", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "8.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/46352348-FA84-41E0-9A7B-B1CDE767DC87_imagesCAE3A2VN.jpg?w=225", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["One end of this dual-sided brow pencil imparts color to fill brows while the other side is a clear wax that helps shape them. As it turns out, both sides of this pencil serve their respective purpose well!", "Ultimate Brows comes in natural-looking shades for brunettes or blondes and stays put so you can count on long-lasting wear. The color goes on sheer so you have to apply added pressure for deeper color, but in a way, that's nice because it makes it harder to overdo it.", "The clear wax helps shape brows while still leaving them soft, and the brush attached to the cap is an added bonus for taming unruly brows.", "The fact that this pencil requires routine sharpening is an inconvenience, but if it\u2019s one you don\u2019t mind then for the price and added features, this pencil isn't too shabby."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 65}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/bulletproof-brows-eyebrow-definer/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyebrow-pencil-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyebrow-pencil-reviews ", "product_names": "Bulletproof Brows Eyebrow Definer", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyebrow Makeup", "brand": "Too Faced", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "30.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/A89DD4FC-85EA-4D38-B8A8-3A9117BC4A4E_TooFaced_BulletproofBrowsEyebrowDefiner.jpg?w=350", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["A set of nicely defined eyebrows can be the perfect finishing touch for a makeup look, but finding the right product to make your brows look their best can be challenging. That's why we're glad Too Faced added another great option to the mix!", "Bulletproof Brows Eyebrow Definer is a wax-like product in a pot that has not one, but two, lids. The top lid is mirrored and flips back to reveal a plastic cap underneath, which flips open sideways. The second cap is designed to keep Bulletproof Brows from drying out, an innovative touch to make sure you get the most out of this product, because it's not cheap!", "Bulletproof Brows has a soft, almost creamy texture, and applies lightly enough that you don't overdo your brows on the first swipe, but you can certainly build up the color for a more dramatic look. Its smooth texture blends easily in between brow hairs, and it dries to a soft finish so the brows don't feel sticky or waxy.", "True to its name, this \"bulletproof\" formula lasts throughout the day, not smudging or fading until you're ready to take it off at night.", "Bulletproof Brows comes with a convenient double-ended applicator that features an angled brush on one end for application and a spoolie brush on the other for blending. So far there are only two shades, a dark brown shade for brunettes and a taupe shade more suited for blonde eyebrows, but both should work on a wide variety of brow colors."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 66}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/brow-sculptor/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyebrow-pencil-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyebrow-pencil-reviews ", "product_names": "Brow Sculptor", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyebrow Makeup", "brand": "Tom Ford", "ingredient": null, "size": "0.01 fl. oz.", "price": "45.00", "claims": "Tom Ford brow sculptor helps you achieve those perfectly groomed brows you're always striving for. It features a unique calligraphy tip that allows for a tailor-made stroke from thin to wide. Remove the opposite-end cap to uncover the grooming brush and twist the cap counterclockwise to reveal the sharpener.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/EDB9B616-ADDF-4518-98D0-1A58EF44B3A2_319mmTF7VLL.jpg?w=300", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["Now this is how you do brows! Although certainly not the cheapest option out there, Tom Ford's Brow Sculptor is definitely on the right track with this brow shading product.", "Brow Sculptor is a wax-type (but not waxy) formula housed in a twist-up tube, and you don't have to sharpen it to get more product. A sharpener is included for those who want an angled edge, but it's optional, which is why this gets high marks from us.", "The brow color itself is smooth-textured and a snap to apply. It comes in a good selection of natural-looking shades, including options for blonde and auburn brows. It blends seamlessly into your natural brow color, and wears well throughout the day.", "As an added bonus, it doesn't make your brows feel sticky, coated in wax, or matted. Although you don't have to spend this much on a good brow product, if you choose to splurge, you'll be getting your money's worth!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 67}
