{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/stencils/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyebrow-pencil-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyebrow-pencil-reviews ", "product_names": "Stencils", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyebrow Makeup", "brand": "Anastasia of Beverly Hills", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "20.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/26E80D26-4C8F-4427-8678-849F42977CBC_AnastasiaStencils.jpg?w=147", "expert_rating": "2", "expert_reviews": ["Anastasia\u2019s classic stencils serve as a guide for shaping and tweezing, which can be helpful for those who are new to brow grooming. The stencils are made of flexible plastic so they can bend with the curvature of your brow area and they are durable enough to use repeatedly. There are five stencils of varying shapes; if you\u2019re new to brow grooming you likely will need help deciding between Petite Arch, Slim High Arch, Medium Arch, High Arch, and Full Arch. Things get a bit more complicated because although the stencils give you a good idea of how to shape brows, they may not fit your eyebrow shape exactly, as everyone\u2019s brows are a little different (and no two brows are 100% identical). This isn\u2019t a bad product, but you might be better off spending your money on a professional brow specialist who can help you find the most flattering brow shape for your face. Then, if desired, you can consider using the Stencils for maintenance at home."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 83}
