iced. Well done, Neutrogena!", "Oh, and as for the honey and coconut mentioned in this eyeliner\u2019s claims: neither ingredient is present in an amount that would noticeably benefit skin around the eyes."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 223}
