Eye Pencil passes the waterproof test and the matte shades hold up well in the waterline (when used to \u201ctightline\u201d the inner rim of your eyelid). The formula is fragrance free, which is a good thing\u2014especially for use so close to the delicate eye area.", "Shades range from sparkly, metallic hues to matte-finish classics. Glossier went outside the box with some colors choices that we don\u2019t normally see for eyeliner, like gingery-orange and mustard-yellow. Obviously, certain hues will look better/show up more richly than others, depending on your skin tone.", "We\u2019re a little surprised that Glossier went the old-school route of an eyeliner pencil that requires manual sharpening (as opposed to more convenient retractable designs). to get it back to a moderately fine point, leaving the pencil almost a fourth of the way used up after just one week. That\u2019s more than the norm\u2014hence, we probably wouldn\u2019t invest in Colorslide Technogel Eye Pencil as our everyday eyeliner, but for those times you want to switch up your eyeliner color, this is a fun way to do it."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 224}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/better-than-sex-eyeliner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews ", "product_names": "Better Than Sex Eyeliner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Too Faced", "ingredient": "Water/Aqua/Eau, Butylene Glycol, Acrylates/Ethylhexyl Acrylate Copolymer, Alcohol, Beheneth-30, Phenoxyethanol, Laureth-21, Aminomethyl Propanol, Black 2 (CI 77266).", "size": "0.02 fl. oz.", "price": "21.00", "claims": "This cutting-edge liquid eyeliner is the easiest you\u2019ll ever use, created to produce a sharp, fluid, smudge-proof line, every time! The combination of our Easy Glide 24-hour waterproof formula and our innovative dual-fiber brush creates an eyeliner so amazing, it\u2019s\u2026Better Than Sex.\n", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/40DC60A0-2F9F-42E1-8C92-A6A1922AE2BE_toofaced.jpg?w=320", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["Better Than Sex Eyeliner follows in the footsteps of Too Faced\u2019s top-rated Better Than Sex Mascara, and we\u2019re happy to report that it\u2019s just as good.", "Equipped with a flexible, narrowly-tapered, brush tip, this liquid eyeliner excels at drawing crisp, precise lines. You have the option of going ultra-thin or creating thicker strokes in layers. Too Faced suggests giving the applicator a little shake before use for maximum saturation. In our experience, doing so delivers super-smooth black color\u2014no skipping, tugging or flaking.", "True to claim, Better Than Sex Eyeliner passed our waterproof test. However, if your eyelids tend to get oily throughout the day, it can end up smudging and fading. Prepping eyelids with a good eyeshadow primer is an easy fix to alleviate that issue.", "By the way, this fragrance-free eyeliner lists alcohol as the fourth ingredient, and while we're often leery of such, in this type of formula it's not major cause for concern in regards to irritation (unless you have ultra-sensitive eyes).", "It all boils down to this: Not everyone finds liquid eyeliners easy to work with and in this case, Better Than Sex Eyeliner may actually be more precise than some like. For others, it will be perfect. Beauty is in the eye of the beholder, quite literally."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 225}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/master-precise-all-day-liquid-eyeliner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews ", "product_names": "Master Precise All Day Liquid Eyeliner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Maybelline New York", "ingredient": "Water, Butylene Glycol, PEG-60 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Styrene/Acrylates/Ammonium Methacrylate Copolymer, Coco-Glucoside, Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Disodium EDTA, Sodium Laureth-12 Sulfate, Trisodium EDTA, Methylparaben, Propylparaben, Iodopropynyl Butylcarbamate. May Contain: Black 2.", "size": "0.03 fl. oz.", "price": "7.99", "claims": "This waterproof eyeliner features an ultra-fine tip that delivers laser-sharp precision for the most defined line.\n\u00a0\n", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/master-precise.jpg?w=202", "expert_rating": "3", "expert_reviews": ["Master Precise All Day Liquid Eyeliner is workable, but it\u2019s not on par with the best eyeliners out there.", "Our main complaint is that the tip of the felt applicator isn\u2019t as saturated with the liquid formula at it needs to be, which makes the color go on less pigmented. It also hinders your ability to draw with precise detail. Shaking the eyeliner upside down and pressing the tip to the inside wall of the cap helps improve the saturation for richer and smoother color\u2026 but it\u2019s annoying to have to do that time after time.", "Once saturated, the flexible tip can draw a thick or thin line interchangeably, based on how you hold it and how much pressure you use (a lighter hand = slimmer lines). The liner sets quickly and stays put, without flaking, smudging or fading.", "The only time we experienced this liner transferring was when we tested it on someone prone to oily eyelids. Using an eyeshadow primer alleviated the issue, and if aren\u2019t prone to oily eyelids, the fragrance-free formula holds up great from the get-go.", "Shade-wise, we appreciate that Master Precise All Day Liquid Eyeliner comes in Cobalt Blue and Forest Brown, in addition to traditional black.", "It boils down to this: Considering there are tons of other great drugstore liquid eyeliners out there, why settle for this one that takes extra effort to work the way it should? Peruse our top-rated eyeliners list for the best of the best instead."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 226}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/bh-liquid-eyeliner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews ", "product_names": "BH Liquid Eyeliner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "BH Cosmetics", "ingredient": "Water/Aqua/Eau,  Acrylates/Ammonium Methacrylate Copolymer,  Dimethicone,  Hyaluronic Acid,  PEG-15 Hydroxystearate,  Phenoxyethanol. May Contain: Iron Oxides", "size": "0.04 fl. oz.", "price": "7.00", "claims": "Go from thin and defined to bold and dramatic in just one stroke! Its long-lasting smudge-proof formula ensures that your look will hold up on even the longest days.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/0F52213F-AE23-4CAE-859C-EA922701E038_bh-cosmetics-liquid-eyeliner.jpg?w=355", "expert_rating": "4", "expert_reviews": ["BH Liquid Eyeliner isn't quite up to snuff with the best eyeliners out there, but it's still a good option.", "The liquid formula is dispensed via a semi-flexible, felt-tip applicator that dispenses smooth, saturated color. The shiny black pigmentation stays put, without smudging or flaking and only minimal fading by day's end.", "The reason this doesn't rate higher is that we just didn't find this as versatile as some of our favorite liquid liners. Despite having a tapered point, it's tricky to get ultra-fine, crisply-defined lines.", "On the other hand, if you like a thicker, bolder eyeliner look, this works just fine. We suppose you could say that beauty is in the eye of the beholder on this one."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 227}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/flyliner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews ", "product_names": "Flyliner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Fenty Beauty", "ingredient": "Aqua/Water/Eau,  Butylene Glycol,  Styrene/Acrylates Copolymer,  Acrylates Copolymer,  Styrene/Acrylates/Ammonium Methacrylate Copolymer,  Beheneth-30,  Pentylene Glycol,  Alcohol,  Caprylyl Glycol,  1, 2-Hexanediol,  Ethylhexylglycerin,  Sodium Laureth-12 Sulfate,  Disodium EDTA,  C11-15 Pareth-7,  Tetrasodium EDTA,  Phenoxyethanol,  Sodium Dehydroacetate,  Potassium Sorbate,  Black 2 (Ci 77266) (Nano).", "size": "0.02 fl. oz.", "price": "20.00", "claims": "Your new be-all, end-all for lining eyes, Flyliner Longwear Liquid Eyeliner delivers everything you want in a liner, and then some. Experience the crisp color intensity of a liquid plus the glide of a gel in one longwearing, water-resistant formula that dries fast and wont fade or transfer until you say when.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/775FAB91-EC7D-4BAD-A652-999175332C21_fenty-beauty-flyliner.jpg?w=318", "expert_rating": "4", "expert_reviews": ["Singer Rihanna's Fenty Beauty line is a bona fide chart-topping success, thanks to formulas that largely live up to (or exceed) expectations. Flyliner doesn't quite hit those lofty heights, but it comes darn close.", "This liquid eyeliner comes in a user-friendly triangular tube that leads to an improved grip for precision lining (bonus: it also stops the tube from rolling off your countertop). It's really easy to get a crisply-defined, clean line because the tube's shape and the fact that the liner tip is pliable without being too flexible.", "The black pigment this lays down is dark and super-saturated, with a high-gloss finish that almost looks shiny from afar (this is not for those who prefer matte finish eyeliner). It's extremely easy to build up more eyeliner without it looking cakey.", "As far as wear goes, it holds up incredibly well throughout the day without a hint of fading; it's still impressive-looking after several hours on.", "The only drawback is that there is some slight \"chipping\" of this eyeliner toward the end of its wear time, meaning it can come off in little flakes. Also, if you have excessively oily eyelids, you'd be best served wearing a good eyeshadow primer underneath. Going without makes this eyeliner prone to smudging, so if you fall into that category, that's something to keep in mind. Otherwise, Flyliner is another hit for Rihanna!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 228}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/always-on-liquid-eyeliner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews ", "product_names": "Always On Liquid Eyeliner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Smashbox", "ingredient": "WaterAquaEau,  Ammonium Styrene/Acrylates Copolymer,  Butylene Glycol,  Alcohol,  Ceteth-20,  Sea SaltMaris SalSel Marin,  Polyglyceryl-3 Disiloxane Dimethicone,  Acrylates/Octylacrylamide Copolymer,  Sodium Hydroxide,  Pentylene Glycol,  Disodium EDTA,  Phenoxyethanol. May Contain: Black 2 (CI 77266),  Iron Oxides (CI 77491,  CI 77492,  CI 77499).", "size": "0.02 fl. oz.", "price": "22.00", "claims": "Smashbox Always On Liquid Eyeliner is an ergonomic liquid eyeliner pen gives you total control and ultimate precision. It easily lines and defines with a high pigment, waterproof formula that lasts for 24 hours.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/664D534A-91D9-49C2-991A-09D6CF97E90F_always-on-liquid-eyeliner.jpg?w=522", "expert_rating": "3", "expert_reviews": ["Smashbox's Always On Liquid Eyeliner does a decent job, but it isn't as impressive as the top-rated eyeliners on the market.", "The liquid formula is dispensed via a felt-tip applicator that's somewhat flexible but not flimsy. For the most part, the color goes on smoothly; occasionally we found ourselves having to apply another layer to ensure fully saturated color. The tapered point allows for a thick or thin line\u2014though it's not as precise as some the latest \"micro\" (very fine) tip applicators.", "Always On Liquid Eyeliner stays put decently well. We did notice our \"wings\" fading by the end of the day a couple times (this seemed to be hit or miss) but smudging and flaking were never issues. The formula withstood our waterproof test (you'll want a good makeup remover to take it off).", "All in all, this isn't a bad option, but because of inconsistent performance, we wouldn't rank it up there with \"must-have\" status.", "*Note: We're not overly concerned about alcohol as the fourth ingredient in this type of formula, but if you have sensitive eyelids it could prove to be irritating."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 229}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/just-gimme-noir-gel-pot-eyeliner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews ", "product_names": "Just Gimme Noir Gel Pot Eyeliner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "CoverGirl", "ingredient": "Trimethylsiloxysilicate,  Isododecane,  Cyclopentasiloxane,  Cyclohexasiloxane,  Ceresin,  Nylon-12,  Ozokerite,  Talc,  Dicaprylyl Carbonate,  Silica Silylate,  Coco Nucifera (Coconut) Oil,  Tocopheryl Acetate,  Propylparaben,  Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract. May Contain: Iron Oxides.", "size": "0.08 fl. oz.", "price": "9.49", "claims": "CoverGirl's Just Gimme Noir Gel Eye Liner is a creamy, whipped formula that glides on easily for up to 24 hours of bold color that won't quit! Apply with its complementary angled brush for the perfect cat eye.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/covergirl-logo.png?w=225", "expert_rating": "2", "expert_reviews": ["CoverGirl's Just Gimme Noir Gel Pot Eyeliner's performance leaves a lot to be desired. In truth, this doesn't come close to matching its competitors, some of which cost even less!", "As is standard for this type of product, it comes in a glass pot with a twist-off lid. A nice touch is that CoverGirl also includes an angled brush to apply this liner.", "Getting the gel liner onto the brush is no problem but getting it successfully onto lids is another issue entirely. The texture is surprisingly dry, which causes it to drag across skin, creating an uneven looking line with faded-looking color. Trying to dip in to the pot again and re-line only makes the problem worse, as the liner still drags, but color gets a bit darker and further emphasizes the uneven line.", "True to claims, this does last a long time, and it's truly water-resistant (a waterproof makeup remover is required to take all of this off at the end of the day). Nice, but not enough to put up with the problematic application competing products typically don't have.", "You'll find much better options on our list of Best Eyeliners."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 230}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/stay-all-day-waterproof-liquid-eyeliner-micro-tip/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews ", "product_names": "Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eyeliner \u2013 Micro Tip", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Stila", "ingredient": "Water,  Ammonium Styrene/Acrylates Copolymer,  Butylene Glycol,  Alcohol,  Beheneth-30,  Acrylates/Octylacrylamide Copolymer,  Phenoxyethanol,  Methylparaben,  Polyglyceryl-3 Disiloxane Dimethicone,  Propylparaben,  Sodium Hydroxide,  Disodium EDTA,  Sodium Benzoate. May Contain: Black 2 (Ci 77266) (Nano).", "size": "0.02 fl. oz.", "price": "22.00", "claims": "This is Stila's number one-selling waterproof liquid eyeliner formula, now with an even finer, ultra-thin tip that lets you line and define with precise strokes. Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eye Liner - Micro Tip is perfect for filling in the spaces between lashes, quickly and easily making lashes appear fuller. The formula glides on with ease, dries quickly, and won't smudge or runfrom day into night.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/6F65D779-C657-467F-9BF8-26C3D69D49C7_stila_logo.jpg?w=146", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["This \"Micro Tip\" version of Stila's original Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eye Liner shares the same great qualities\u2014just with an even finer tip. Among the high notes, it's a cinch to create ultra-thin lines and the perfect cat eye, plus the liner stays in place all day just like the name implies.", "The combination of the liquid formula and slim, felt-tip applicator results in saturated-black, fluid lines that stay solid morning to night (even on oily eyelids). The applicator is not only thinner, but also shorter than the original liner, allowing for even more precise control. As Stila puts it, \"Micro Tip is perfect for filling in the spaces between lashes, quickly and easily making lashes appear fuller.\"", "While precision is Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eye \u2013 Micro Tip's forte, you can also easily build thicker lines without skipping, dragging, or tugging. The liner sets quickly, doesn't smudge or flake, and yes, it's even waterproof.", "By the way, we should mention that while this performs similarly to the original All Day Waterproof Liquid Eye Liner, the formulas are actually slightly different. This version contains alcohol as the fourth ingredient, and while we're often leery of such, in this type of formula it's not major cause for concern in regards to irritation (unless you have ultra-sensitive eyes).", "The bottom line: This is an excellent liquid liner for anyone who likes an intricate cat eye or ultra-thin lines. Bravo, Stila!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 231}
