 "The fragrance-free, gel-cream formula is equally impressive with rich pigmentation that stays put, resists fading, and even holds up in water. Rounding things out, the shade range is on point with hues of black, brown, blue, plum, green and gray\u2014some are matte; others have a subtle hint of metallic sheen.", "Beautifully done, Shiseido!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 237}
