{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/shaping-secret-eyelift-wand/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews%26p%3D2 ", "product_names": "Shaping Secret Eyelift Wand", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Mally Beauty", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "25.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/C8C853C3-7085-4929-B88D-FF82ED28318D_11dEsOwumgL.jpg?w=29", "expert_rating": "3", "expert_reviews": [" Shaping Secret Eyelift Wand is an automatic retractable cream-to-powder eyeliner pencil that\u2019s reminiscent of a calligraphy pen. The biggest plus is that the texture, finish, and color of this product make it useful for lining the eyes and filling in the brows. The opposite end of the pencil has a pointed sponge-tip applicator pre-loaded with a coordinating shade of dark powder eyeshadow.", " Mally Beauty\u2019s gimmicky claim that this product is an \u201ceye lift in a pen\u201d shouldn\u2019t be taken seriously. Although the angled pencil tip offers a unique design that takes the guesswork out of creating a flattering, upturned cat-eye look, the lifting effect is at best minimal, and not everyone looks good with this type of eyelining technique.", " If you want a multi-purpose pencil liner that works equally well for brows and eyelining, give this a go\u2014but don\u2019t buy it because you expect it to make you look (even vaguely) like you\u2019ve had an eye lift.", " Pros:", " Cons: "], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 338}
