{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/liquid-liner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews%26p%3D3 ", "product_names": "Liquid Liner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Cargo Cosmetics", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "22.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/CDFF1942-4CC2-461D-AC62-D2B195D78923_Cargo_LiquidLiner.jpg?w=28", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["Although this is pricey, it happens to be one of the best, easiest-to-use liquid liners you\u2019re likely to find. Packaged like a felt-tip pen, the applicator has a narrow point so you can get an ultra-thin line. Alternatively, you can use the side of the brush for a thicker line. In either case, application is even and pigment-rich, the formula dries quickly, and it stays in place exceptionally well. Only one shade is available, but unless you have very pale skin, you can\u2019t go wrong with classic black!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 414}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/long-wear-gel-eyeliner/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeliner-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeliner-reviews%26p%3D3 ", "product_names": "Long-Wear Gel Eyeliner", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeliner", "brand": "Bobbi Brown", "ingredient": "Isododecane,  Cyclopentasiloxane,  Polyethylene,  Trimethylsiloxysilicate,  Disteardimonium Hectorite,  Propylene Carbonate,  Lecithin,  Phenyl Trimethicone,  Hydrogenated Polyisobutene,  Methicone,  Barium Sulfate,  BHT,  Phenoxyethanol. May contain: Iron Oxides,  Mica,  Titanium Dioxide,  Blue 1 Lake,  Carmine,  Chromium Oxide Greens,  Manganese Violet,  Yellow 5 Lake,  Chromium Hydroxide Green,  Bismuth Oxychloride,  Ultramarines,  Ferric Ferrocyanide.", "size": "0.10 fl. oz.", "price": "25.00", "claims": "A true original. This award-winning long-wearing eyeliner offers the precision of liquid liner with the ease of a gel-based formulaall with 12 hours of waterproof and sweat- and humidity-resistant wear.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/19E9D5F8-2A3C-4DEC-A22A-023D1C65E161_310b9sWT2eL.jpg?w=350", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["Long-Wear Gel Eyeliner is a longstanding Bobbi Brown favorite and for good reason: This fragrance-free eyeliner comes in an extensive (20+!) array of shades to suit just about anyone's taste, and true to name, it sets to a long-wearing, budge-proof finish!", "Housed in a small gloss pot, Long-Wear Gel Eyeliner has a gel-cream texture that you apply with a brush (sold separately, or you can use your own eyeliner brush). It goes on smoothly without skipping or dragging, a trait which makes lining the eyes a breeze. More to love, the formula holds up to its claims of water/sweat-resistance for worry-free wear, even during the heat and humidity of summer.", "Although all of the shades offer saturated pigmentation, the ones without shimmer apply the richest. The selection of shades are often changed up seasonally, but the core assortment of blacks, charcoal brown, and steely grays remain staples and are perfect!", "You'll notice some shades are categorized as \"Double Lining\" on Bobbi Brown's website, but after speaking to the brand's reps, we discovered there is nothing different about the formula. \"Double lining\" simply refers to a technique that Brown uses when applying a gel-cream eyeliner and then layering a powder over it to intensify and/or set the color. This is an option, but one we find superfluous given how tenacious and dramatic Brown's gel eyeliner can look on its own.", "In the end, Long-Wear Gel Eyeliner earns accolades as an extraordinary product that not only lasts the workday through, but comes in a gorgeous assortment of colors. Thanks Bobbi!", "Note: As with all such eyeliners, the formula is prone to drying out if you aren't good about recapping the jar tightly after each use."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 415}
