dy shades, as well as some more everyday wearable colors. All have glimmering shine that can highlight wrinkly lids, but if that's not an issue for you, Eye Pigment can be a fun addition to your makeup stash."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 579}
