re. They wear well on their own or can be layered over another shadow.", "The only time the fallout is a major issue is if you try to manipulate the shadow after it has set (i.e. by applying a powder shadow over it).", "Most of the shades deliver stunning, solid metallic color packed with glitter of varying particle sizes. The exception is the Ulta-exclusive shade \"Ballet Baby\" which goes on sheer and doesn't perform as well as the rest overall.", "That aside, Magnificent Metals Glitter & Glow Liquid Eyeshadow delivers on its promise of \"incredible luster\" and is a nice alternative to glitter shadows of yesteryear. We'll cheers to that!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 583}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/colorstay-creme-eye-shadow/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-reviews ", "product_names": "ColorStay Creme Eye Shadow", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow", "brand": "Revlon", "ingredient": "Isododecane,  Trimethylsiloxysilicate,  Isohexadecane,  Polyethylene,  Dimethicone,  Synthetic Fluorphlogopite,  Calcium Sodium Borosilicate,  Calcium Aluminum Borosilicate,  Silica,  Adipic Acid/Neopentyl Glycol Crosspolymer,  Nylon-12,  Sorbitan Trioleate,  BHT,  Benzoic Acid. May Contain: Mica,  Titanium Dioxide,  Iron Oxides,  Carmine,  Aluminum Powder,  Ultramarines,  Chromium Hydroxide Green,  Chromium Oxide Greens,  Ferric Ferrocyanide,  Ferric Ammonium Ferrocyanide,  Bismuth Oxychloride,  Blue 1 Lake,  Yellow 5 Lake,  Manganese Violet,  Tin Oxide", "size": "0.18 fl. oz.", "price": "6.99", "claims": "Luxurious, longwear crme eye shadow with a pro-inspired built-in-brush designed for easy, mess free application. ", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/87250796-ECCD-4016-8224-6D38BF23230F_RevlonColorStayCremeShadow.jpg?w=500", "expert_rating": "4", "expert_reviews": ["ColorStay Cr\u00e8me Eye Shadow offers buildable, flake-proof color that comes in matte or sparkly finishes. With oily eyelids, we did experience fading and creasing as the day wore on, but otherwise this shadow performs well.", "ColorStay Cr\u00e8me Eye Shadow comes in a screw-top jar with a built-in small, removable brush. We found ourselves applying this with our fingertips or a full-size brush instead, but it's nice that Revlon included the option. Whichever way you apply it, the formula glides on silky smooth and allows ample time for blending.", "Once set, the fragrance-free formula resists smearing. As mentioned earlier, oily skin types may experience fading and creasing, but this didn't seem to be much of an issue where normal to dry skin was concerned.", "All in all, we'd say this a good but not quite great cream shadow at a reasonable price."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 584}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/color-tattoo-eye-chrome/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-reviews ", "product_names": "Color Tattoo Eye Chrome", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow", "brand": "Maybelline New York", "ingredient": "Isododecane, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Dimethicone, Tribehenin, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, C18-36 Acid Glycol Ester, C18-36 Acid Triglyceride, Phenoxyethanol, Silica, Tin Oxide. May Contain: CI 75470 / Carmine, CI 77000 / Aluminum Powder, CI 77007 / Ultramarines, CI 77288 / Chromium Oxide Greens, CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides, CI 77510 / Ferric Ferrocyanide, CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, Mica.", "size": "0.11 fl. oz.", "price": "7.99", "claims": "Metallic intensity and tattoo tenacity brilliantly combine to saturate your lids in liquid chrome shine for up to 24 hours.\n", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/A87A3559-A621-4BAD-B49D-AC5C128BCB4D_MaybellineCTChrome.jpg?w=141", "expert_rating": "2", "expert_reviews": ["Color Tattoo Eye Chrome is Maybelline's take on cream eyeshadow in a tube, and though it certainly lives up to some of its claims, overall it's just not worth picking up\u2014even at its bargain price!", "This shadow is packaged much like a lip gloss, in a clear plastic tube with a doe-foot wand applicator. It has a smooth, almost mousse-like texture that glides across eye with ease initially, and has bold, saturated, metallic color.", "If you don't quickly apply a sufficient amount of this product as needed to cover your entire eye area, you will quickly run into problems because the formula dries very quickly. In other words, you have little time to blend, and if you want to put more shadow over what you first applied the result is clumpy, uneven coverage.", "When it comes to wear time, this does last all day without fading or flaking (Maybelline claims this lasts up to a full 24 hours, but you definitely should not be wearing your makeup that long, as the ingredients in eyeshadow shouldn't be left on overnight if you want to avoid red puffy eyes in the morning.", "When it comes time to remove this shadow, it takes quite a bit of effort\u2014even with waterproof makeup remover. You'll end up having to tug at your delicate eye area, which is not a good idea because that can lead to sagging and wrinkles.", "Although one of the better priced cream shadows on the market, and one that doesn't slip or fade like many of its competitors it is a tempting buy but because of blending difficulties and the effort it takes to remove it, we suggest you stay away. You'll find better options on our list of Best Eyeshadows."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 585}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/superhero-eye-transforming-anti-aging-super-palette/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-reviews ", "product_names": "Superhero Eye Transforming Anti-Aging Super Palette", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow", "brand": "IT Cosmetics", "ingredient": "Confidence,  Magical,  Aura,  Superstar,  & Fearless: Mica,  Magnesium Stearate,  Hydrogenated Polyisobutene,  Dimethicone,  Isopropyl Myristate,  Polybutene,  Phenoxyethanol,  Tocopheryl Acetate,  Retinyl Palmitate,  Tocopherol,  Magnesium Ascorbyl Phosphate,  Aqua/Water/Eau,  Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract,  Hydrolyzed Silk,  Hydrolyzed Collagen,  Glycerin,  Butylene Glycol,  Carbomer,  Polysorbate 20,  Palmitoyl Oligopeptide,  Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7,  [+/-: Titanium Dioxide (Ci 77891),  Iron Oxides (Ci 77499,  77492,  77491),  Manganese Violet (Ci 77742),  Ultramarines (Ci 77007)]. Pow,  Limitless,  Powerful,  Unstoppable,  Bold,  Daring,  Superhero: Mica,  Dimethicone,  Magnesium Stearate,  Phenoxyethanol,  Tocopheryl Acetate,  Aqua/Water/Eau,  Cholesteryl Oleyl Carbonate,  Cholesteryl Nonanoate,  Cholesteryl Chloride,  Retinyl Palmitate,  Tocopherol,  Magnesium Ascorbyl Phosphate,  Hydrolyzed Silk,  Hydrolyzed Collagen,  Glycerin,  Euterpe Oleracea Fruit Extract,  Butylene Glycol,  Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract,  Carbomer,  Polysorbate 20,  Palmitoyl Oligopeptide,  Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7,  Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil,  Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract,  Hyaluronic Acid,  Niacinamide,  Olea Europaea (Olive) Leaf Extract,  Oryza Sativa (Rice) Extract,  Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract,  Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil,  Perfluorodecalin,  [+/-: Titanium Dioxide (Ci 77891),  Iron Oxides (Ci 77499,  Ci 77492,  Ci 77491),  Manganese Violet (Ci 77942),  Ultramarines (Ci 77007)].", "size": "0.54 fl. oz.", "price": "42.00", "claims": "Transform your eyes with this must-have, universally flattering, game-changing palette featuring 12 all-new Superhero-inspired shades. Developed with plastic surgeons, each anti-aging, ultra-luxe eyeshadow is formulated with hydrolyzed collagen, silk, peptides and antioxidants, plus innovative Superhero Pigment Power Technology for super smooth, super skin-loving, super saturated shades that last from day to night! ", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/900F49A5-23E6-48A9-A296-04E7788E7AFB_IT-Cosmetics-resized.jpg?w=300", "expert_rating": "3", "expert_reviews": ["Makeup with skincare benefits is a growing category, often with foundation or other complexion products. But eyeshadow? That's the hook with IT Cosmetics' Superhero Eye Transforming Anti-Aging Super Palette. Although it has some good qualities, it doesn't exactly leap tall buildings in a single bound when it comes to having anything to do with anti-aging claims.", "This 12-shade, fragrance-free palette comes in a plastic compact that's brilliantly set up: At the top are three larger pans containing what the brand calls \"Eye Foundation\" (essentially, base shades), and then nine smaller pans divided into groups of three shadows each:  \"Nudes,\" (beige, soft pink, and tan) \"Neutrals,\" (light gold, dusty lavender, rosy pink) and \"Liners\" (navy, medium brown, and black). This type of arrangement makes choosing colors and combinations much easier, so job well done there!", "The shades come in a mix of satin, shimmer, and matte options (all the liner shades are matte), all with a silky texture that's easy to pick up on a brush (we should note: This does not come with its own brush). They apply smoothly and evenly with no patchiness.", "The problem is that all the shades (particularly the darker ones) have a noticeable amount of messy, powdery fallout. Even tapping your brush thoroughly before application still results in color getting all over cheekbones and other areas of your face. You'll likely find yourself having to brush off your face, which is not an easy task especially if you apply foundation beforehand!", "However, once you do get the colors you want applied and the potential fallout mess cleaned up, these shadows wear well without fading or creasing throughout the day, and are easily removed.", "So what about those skincare claims that accompany this palette? These powder shadows contain some good ingredients (antioxidants, hydrolyzed silk, and even a couple of peptides), but in a powder compact they won't have much impact on aging skin. That's particularly true of the antioxidants, which will lose their effectiveness over time because in this packaging they're routinely exposed to light and air, which causes antioxidants to destabilize.", "While we certainly admire IT Cosmetics for adding these ingredients, the claims (including the association with plastic surgeons, which may well be true but what does that have to do with makeup?) are overstated; you're better served by a serum, moisturizer, eye cream, or even foundation that contains these ingredients."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 586}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/liquid-moondust-eyeshadow/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-reviews ", "product_names": "Liquid Moondust Eyeshadow", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow", "brand": "Urban Decay", "ingredient": "Water,  Butylene Glycol,  Synthetic Fluorphlogopite,  Calcium Sodium Borosilicate,  Dicaprylyl Carbonate,  Silica,  Talc,  Betaine,  Aluminum Calcium Sodium Silicate,  Alumina,  Phenoxyethanol,  Ethylhexylglycerin,  Polysorbate 20,  Dimethicone,  Sorbitan Sesquioleate,  Calcium Aluminum Borosilicate,  Gellan Gum,  Sodium Acrylate/Sodium Acryloyldimethyl Taurate Copolymer,  Isohexadecane,  Dimethicone Crosspolymer,  Tin Oxide,  Polyglyceryl-4 Isostearate,  Cetyl PEG/PPG-10/1 Dimethicone,  Hexyl Laurate,  Polysorbate 80,  Sorbitan Oleate,  Isopropyl Titanium Triisostearate,  Tocopherol. [+/- (All Shades May Contain): Mica,  CI 77491/ 77492/77499 (Iron Oxides),  CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide),  CI 77163 (Bismuth Oxychloride),  CI 77510 (Ferric Ferrocyanide)].", "size": "0.17 fl. oz.", "price": "22.00", "claims": "A super-versatile cream version of the innovative formula you know and love. Similar to our pressed Moondust Eyeshadows, Liquid Moondust contains microfine bits of iridescent sparkle and lush, 3-D metallics for a gorgeous, diamond-like effect. Its innovative, lightweight formula feels cool and wears comfortably. Create subtle eye looks or layer and build the formula for more intense, 3-D metallic effects. Whether you want to add just a hint of sparkle at the lash line or layer color over the lid, the slim, precise brush does it all. For all-over sparkle, lay the color down quickly and blend it out. \r\n", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/DD3896BE-37BB-466A-82B4-8F17C11D4EEF_URBAN-DECAY-2014.png?w=201", "expert_rating": "3", "expert_reviews": ["Low-key is definitely not the phrase to describe Urban Decay's Liquid Moondust Eyeshadow, but it would be a fun and different dramatic eyeshadow option if its performance matched its claims!", "Fragrance free Liquid Moondust Eyeshadow comes in a clear plastic tube with a paintbrush-like applicator. Though Urban Decay labels this a cream, the texture is much closer to that of a gel, down to it having a cooling effect on skin when applied (good news though\u2014the cooling effect is not the result of any skin-aggravating ingredients).", "Each of the options available features a sheer color base (such as iridescent green, deep purple, and bright blue) loaded with glitter in the corresponding shade. The result is a wet, high-shine appearance that works well for party or fashion looks. Though Urban Decay says this can be used for a subtle effect, people will definitely know you're wearing quite a bit of glitter! It's just hard to make glitter look subtle!", "The gel texture makes this easy to apply and blend, and it dries down without feeling tight, which is characteristic of some gel products. Creasing is not apparent since there's so much glitter, and it doesn't fade even through a standard workday.", "There are a couple of drawback to note: The first is that the formula has a tendency to clump, which means sometimes when you remove the applicator from the tube, a chunk of glitter gel comes out. The other drawback is that the glitter migrates to other areas of the face, even if you don't touch your eyes throughout the day.", "While a fun product in concept, the caveats mean this isn't a product we recommend with much enthusiasm."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 587}
