{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/pure-color-stay-on-shadow-paint/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-reviews%26p%3D2 ", "product_names": "Pure Color Stay-On Shadow Paint", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow", "brand": "Estee Lauder", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "24.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/6E310438-D2CC-4A5C-B7D6-3A695F476F3C_41vPX99xzyL.jpg?w=500", "expert_rating": "4", "expert_reviews": ["Pure Color Stay-On Shadow Paint is Estee Lauder's foray into the world of cream eyeshadows, and it's a decent addition, although not without some drawbacks. This glass pot\u2013packaged shadow has an exceptionally creamy, almost mousse-like, texture. It applies easily and smoothly, and sets quickly, but not so quickly that you can't blend adequately before it dries.", "Here's the best part: This doesn't crease! It also wears well for several hours without fading, and comes off easily with either a waterproof or long-wearing makeup remover.", "Now to those drawbacks: Every shade has some level of shimmer or glitter, and for most of the shades that level is quite high. That's not bad if that's what you want, but it's limiting if you're looking for matte options. The glitter also tends to migrate to other areas of your face after a few hours of wear. Were it not for this issue, this would have earned our highest rating!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 661}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/countless-color-pigments/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-reviews%26p%3D2 ", "product_names": "Countless Color Pigments", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow", "brand": "Stila", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "22.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/0B1CD9DC-0DE7-4658-A2BC-EE320DA28BA1_51Z6ckqkXwL.jpg?w=422", "expert_rating": "2", "expert_reviews": ["Each of these pressed-powder eyeshadow compacts has a unique, multicolor, tie-dye pattern, which Stila hypes as \"innovative.\" It may look innovative, but performance-wise there is no innovation to be found!", "While the powder does have a smooth texture and a satin finish that clings well, these kitschy shadows are more trouble than they're worth. True to claim, there are \"countless color combinations\" that can be achieved with these eyeshadows, but unless you're a very patient person with a steady hand and a stash of small brushes and you want to spend time figuring out which ones to combine, it becomes a frustrating memory game you will most likely lose. There is simply no guarantee you'll be able to get the color combination on one eyelid to match what's on the other eyelid.", "For better eyeshadow options\u2014including Stila's eyeshadow singles, check out our Best Products."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 662}
