ny cream shadows\u2014in fact, once this sets, it resists creasing or fading (even on oily lids or especially humid conditions).", "The color selection offers options for those seeking neutral shades to use for a base color, crease or to highlight the brow bone. (The deeper shades also work well when used as eyeliner.) From bone white to deep aubergine and bronze shades, there is certain to be something for those in any skin tone range. There is a mix of matte and satin finishes\u2014those with shimmer are mostly on the low to moderate side of shine.", "For its tenacious wear time, beautiful range of color options and superior performance, Bobbi Brown's Long-Wear Cream Shadow earns our highest rating. Here's a quick tip for even longer wear: Layer this under a matte powder shadow. The combination will make this formula quite water-resistant (so much so that you'll likely need an oil-based makeup remover to take it off at the end of the day)."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 722}
