{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/mono-eyeshadow/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-reviews%26p%3D3 ", "product_names": "Mono Eyeshadow", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow", "brand": "Clarins", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "21.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/0929F253-610B-4967-B8F5-BA20FD3C28F3_Clarins_MonoEyeshadow.jpg?w=522", "expert_rating": "5", "expert_reviews": ["We wish this eyeshadow were available in a wider range of workable shades, because its very smooth texture applies beautifully without flaking. Color saturation is on the sheer side. Most of the colors are shiny, and there are some purple and greens to avoid. Overall, this is a great eyeshadow to check out if your budget permits, although you don\u2019t need to spend this much for a quality powder eyeshadow."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 799}
