ng or fading until night's end.", "Shade-wise, there's a mix of trendy hues, pastel colors, and classic neutrals. Most sets come in complementary colors, and you can pick between shimmering metallic or matte finishes.", "We have to point out that not all the colors go on as richly as they appear (by the time you blend them, the pigmentation sheers a bit). However, you can easily layer the color for more intensity.", "Overall, we've got to hand it to L'Oreal on this one\u2026Infallible Paints Eye Shadow surprised us in all the right ways!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 842}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/superhero-eye-transforming-anti-aging-super-palette/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-palette-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-palette-reviews ", "product_names": "Superhero Eye Transforming Anti-Aging Super Palette", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow Palette", "brand": "IT Cosmetics", "ingredient": "Confidence,  Magical,  Aura,  Superstar,  & Fearless: Mica,  Magnesium Stearate,  Hydrogenated Polyisobutene,  Dimethicone,  Isopropyl Myristate,  Polybutene,  Phenoxyethanol,  Tocopheryl Acetate,  Retinyl Palmitate,  Tocopherol,  Magnesium Ascorbyl Phosphate,  Aqua/Water/Eau,  Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract,  Hydrolyzed Silk,  Hydrolyzed Collagen,  Glycerin,  Butylene Glycol,  Carbomer,  Polysorbate 20,  Palmitoyl Oligopeptide,  Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7,  [+/-: Titanium Dioxide (Ci 77891),  Iron Oxides (Ci 77499,  77492,  77491),  Manganese Violet (Ci 77742),  Ultramarines (Ci 77007)]. Pow,  Limitless,  Powerful,  Unstoppable,  Bold,  Daring,  Superhero: Mica,  Dimethicone,  Magnesium Stearate,  Phenoxyethanol,  Tocopheryl Acetate,  Aqua/Water/Eau,  Cholesteryl Oleyl Carbonate,  Cholesteryl Nonanoate,  Cholesteryl Chloride,  Retinyl Palmitate,  Tocopherol,  Magnesium Ascorbyl Phosphate,  Hydrolyzed Silk,  Hydrolyzed Collagen,  Glycerin,  Euterpe Oleracea Fruit Extract,  Butylene Glycol,  Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract,  Carbomer,  Polysorbate 20,  Palmitoyl Oligopeptide,  Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7,  Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil,  Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract,  Hyaluronic Acid,  Niacinamide,  Olea Europaea (Olive) Leaf Extract,  Oryza Sativa (Rice) Extract,  Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract,  Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil,  Perfluorodecalin,  [+/-: Titanium Dioxide (Ci 77891),  Iron Oxides (Ci 77499,  Ci 77492,  Ci 77491),  Manganese Violet (Ci 77942),  Ultramarines (Ci 77007)].", "size": "0.54 fl. oz.", "price": "42.00", "claims": "Transform your eyes with this must-have, universally flattering, game-changing palette featuring 12 all-new Superhero-inspired shades. Developed with plastic surgeons, each anti-aging, ultra-luxe eyeshadow is formulated with hydrolyzed collagen, silk, peptides and antioxidants, plus innovative Superhero Pigment Power Technology for super smooth, super skin-loving, super saturated shades that last from day to night! ", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/900F49A5-23E6-48A9-A296-04E7788E7AFB_IT-Cosmetics-resized.jpg?w=300", "expert_rating": "3", "expert_reviews": ["Makeup with skincare benefits is a growing category, often with foundation or other complexion products. But eyeshadow? That's the hook with IT Cosmetics' Superhero Eye Transforming Anti-Aging Super Palette. Although it has some good qualities, it doesn't exactly leap tall buildings in a single bound when it comes to having anything to do with anti-aging claims.", "This 12-shade, fragrance-free palette comes in a plastic compact that's brilliantly set up: At the top are three larger pans containing what the brand calls \"Eye Foundation\" (essentially, base shades), and then nine smaller pans divided into groups of three shadows each:  \"Nudes,\" (beige, soft pink, and tan) \"Neutrals,\" (light gold, dusty lavender, rosy pink) and \"Liners\" (navy, medium brown, and black). This type of arrangement makes choosing colors and combinations much easier, so job well done there!", "The shades come in a mix of satin, shimmer, and matte options (all the liner shades are matte), all with a silky texture that's easy to pick up on a brush (we should note: This does not come with its own brush). They apply smoothly and evenly with no patchiness.", "The problem is that all the shades (particularly the darker ones) have a noticeable amount of messy, powdery fallout. Even tapping your brush thoroughly before application still results in color getting all over cheekbones and other areas of your face. You'll likely find yourself having to brush off your face, which is not an easy task especially if you apply foundation beforehand!", "However, once you do get the colors you want applied and the potential fallout mess cleaned up, these shadows wear well without fading or creasing throughout the day, and are easily removed.", "So what about those skincare claims that accompany this palette? These powder shadows contain some good ingredients (antioxidants, hydrolyzed silk, and even a couple of peptides), but in a powder compact they won't have much impact on aging skin. That's particularly true of the antioxidants, which will lose their effectiveness over time because in this packaging they're routinely exposed to light and air, which causes antioxidants to destabilize.", "While we certainly admire IT Cosmetics for adding these ingredients, the claims (including the association with plastic surgeons, which may well be true but what does that have to do with makeup?) are overstated; you're better served by a serum, moisturizer, eye cream, or even foundation that contains these ingredients."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 843}
