you're looking for a one-stop-shop palette for statement eyes, Kat von D's Serpentina Eyeshadow Palette delivers!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 844}
