Tocopheryl Acetate,  Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891),  Iron Oxides (CI 77491,  CI 77492,  CI 77499).", "size": "0.21 fl. oz.", "price": "26.00", "claims": "We hit refresh on the monochromatic world of contouring to give it a rich new perspective! With artistically curated shades, this collection features four all-matte palettes, specially designed to enhance your eye shape and color. And of course, each shade is formulated in Kats high-pigment, silky and blendable eyeshadow formula.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/07D2E431-8F15-46B0-AF33-0CD16E1D7519_Kat-Von-D-Brand.jpg?w=222", "expert_rating": "3", "expert_reviews": ["Kat Von D's Shade + Light Eye Contour Quads are composed of four matte eyeshadows to enhance eye shape and color. Performance-wise, they get mixed reviews on the web. You'll find customers who extol nothing but the highest regard, versus others that complain about issues with blending and creasing. It turns out those polarizing reviews are justified. Some shades don't blend as smoothly as others, and creasing was an issue for us as well (when not paired a primer).", "However, it's not all doom and gloom\u2014these fragrance-free shadows deliver appreciable color payoff. Using an eyeshadow primer (here's the one we paired it with) intensifies the pigmentation, but even without it, the shades do well enough on their own.", "The creasing issue is another case where pairing the shadows with a primer helped significantly. Without primer, we experienced creasing a few hours into wear, but with primer, it lasted all night, zero fading or creasing. Still, a great eyeshadow will go the distance without an assist from primer.", "Shade-wise, the combinations of colors were hit or miss for us. We found \"Rust\" and \"Sage\" less cohesive than \"Smoke\" or \"Plum\" to create a unified look, but given that color preference is such a personal choice, we're not holding that against the rating.", "Considering the variability of how well Shade + Light Eye Contour Quads blend and other pros and cons, we fall in the middle on this one. For eyeshadow quads with solid performance, see our Best Eyeshadows Palettes list\u2014and don't forget to share your experience with this shadow in the Community Reviews section of this review!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 845}
