ides,  Ultramarines. XII: Dimethicone,  Talc,  Calcium Sodium Borosilicate,  Kaolin,  Trimethylsiloxysilicate,  Polypropylsilsequioxane,  Zinc Stearate,  Zea Mays (Corn) Starch,  Caprylyl Glycol,  Pentylene Glycol,  Sorbitan Sesquiisostearate,  Sodium Dehydroacetate,  Tocopheryl Acetate,  Octyldodecyl Stearoyl Stearate,  Tin Oxide. May Contain: Mica,  Titanium Dioxide,  Iron Oxides,  Ultramarines.", "size": "0.85 fl. oz.", "price": "59.00", "claims": "TWELVE SHARP Matte, shimmer, and style. Everyday neutrals meet eight accents in this full-spectrum wardrobe of curated shadows. Eyes. Customized.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/6CB0D025-CDF1-4799-BC6A-71E9A0C2F341_NARS-NARSissist-LAmour-Palette-sq.png?w=600", "expert_rating": "4", "expert_reviews": ["Eyeshadow palettes offer a great way to mix and match various shades for a range of looks, and that's the appeal of NARS' NARSissist L'Amour, Toujours L'Amour Eyeshadow Palette (what a name!). For the most part, this palette lives up to expectations, albeit with one drawback that keeps it just out of striking range of earning our top rating.", "NARSissist L'Amour, Toujours L'Amour (which translates to \"Love, Always Love\") comes in the brand's standard sleek black packaging. Specifically, a mirrored compact that holds 12 shades of powder eyeshadow. (Bonus: These shades are all brand new to the NARS collection, so no need to worry about already owning them.)", "The top four shades are larger in size than the bottom eight shades; the larger shades include neutral beige, gold, brown, and charcoal, all colors designed to be used more frequently than the smaller eight \"accent\" shades. Most of the shades are actually fairly neutral, save for a bright copper and a deep blue that are among the accents. Various finishes are also in the mix, from satin to shimmer, with four mattes as well.", "Across the board, the initial issue with these shadows (and the reason they didn't earn a higher rating) is that their application is quite sheer to start. A single swipe of any of the 12 shades, no matter their color or texture, results in a light wash of color on lids. Even using a primer underneath, the initial application doesn't yield much color payoff. We like that the colors are buildable, but you have to take care when applying multiple layers of the shimmer shades, as some fallout can occur.", "Once applied, however, these shadows are standouts when it comes to performance. The fragrance-free formulas wore well throughout a standard workday without fading or flaking, and there was minimal creasing without primer. When we went to take off our makeup at the end of the day, the shadows appeared nearly as smooth as when we first put them on! Impressive? You bet!", "The shades are workable for a wide range of skin tones, and offer enough neutral options that everyday basic eye looks are simple to put together. The small number of brighter colors offer a nice accent to an eye look (as they're intended to do), and mean this is a palette than can easily transfer your look from day to night without the need for additional products.", "Overall, the NARS NARSissist L'Amour, Toujours L'Amour palette has a lot to offer. Once you get past the initial sheer application and if you layer carefully, it's a palette that performs well, and is one we can definitely set a loving gaze on!"], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 846}
{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/artistry-eye-shadow-kit/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-palette-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-palette-reviews ", "product_names": "Artistry Eye Shadow Kit", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow Palette", "brand": "Ulta", "ingredient": "Talc,  Dimethicone,  Magnesium Stearate,  Silica,  Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter,  Triisostearyl Citrate,  Methylparaben,  Butylparaben,  Phenoxyethanol. May Contain: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891),  Iron Oxides (CI 77491,  CI 77492,  CI 77499),  Yellow 5 (CI 19140),  Chromium Hydroxide Green (CI 77289),  Red 40 Lake (CI 16035),  Black 2 (CI 77266),  Ferric Ammonium Ferrocyanide (CI 77510),  Manganese Violet (CI 77742),  Chromium Oxide Greens (CI 77288),  Ultramarines (CI 77007),  Blue 1 (CI 42090).", "size": "0.15 fl. oz.", "price": "20.00", "claims": "Ulta Artistry Eye Shadow Kit includes 3 eye shadow palettes. Each palette combines a range of matte and shimmer textures for all occasions. Beautiful wave pressing pattern makes this set an extra special gift or luxurious treat for yourself.", "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/D9375D38-2339-4A64-8434-62E61864183B_Ulta-AristryEyeShadowKit-sq.png?w=600", "expert_rating": "2", "expert_reviews": ["If you're a self-described makeup junkie, the first thing you'll likely notice about Ulta's fragrance-free Artistry Eye Shadow Kit is that it looks very similar to another product, namely Hourglass Cosmetics' Modernist Eyeshadow Palette. So is Ulta's option a more budget-friendly version of a high-end offering (the Modernist Palette costs close to $60)? In some ways, the answer is yes\u2026though this has enough drawbacks (including some it shares with its higher-end cousin) that it's a largely disappointing option.", "Like the Hourglass Modernist, the shades for Artistry Eye Shadow Kit are arranged in a wave-like pattern that's flat-out gorgeous; it truly does resemble sand art! However, one of the biggest differences between the two products is the packaging. The Artistry Eye Shadow Kit comes in a cardboard container that includes three separate palettes with five shades each; the Modernist Eyeshadow Palette consists of a single, larger palette of five shades.", "Pretty packaging and embossing aside, how does Ulta's Artistry Eye Shadow Kit  perform? Though the texture is soft and easy to pick up on a brush (it isn't overly powdery), getting color to show up, even with the most intense shades, takes a bit of work. The initial application is quite sheer if you don't use a primer, and requires multiple layers to get visible color. Once the color does show up, it lasts for about seven hours without fading.", "The three palette options offered in the kit are very attractive; they include a set with plum and bronze shades, another with forest green, soft brown, and gold shades, and one with navy blue, gold, and chocolate brown tones.", "The color combinations are compelling, but each set offers at least two glitter/sparkle shades that flake and fall out as the day goes on. We found flecks of glitter under our eye and on our cheekbones by the end of its wear time, and even some fallout as we were applying them (this is an issue with the Modernist Palette as well). If you're going to rock a glitter eyeshadow, the least it should do is stay in place!", "Though Ulta's Artistry Eye Shadow Kit is pretty in the pan, its sheer application and the inclusion of several glitter-flecked shades that flake mean that even for its bargain price, it's far from the best option available. You'll find superior products on our list of Best Eyeshadow Palettes."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 847}
