{"product_links": "https://www.beautypedia.com/products/le-prisme-eyeshadow-quartet/?archive_search=%2Fmakeup%2Feyes%2Feyeshadow-palette-reviews%2F%3Fsize%3D96%26makeup_group%5B0%5D%3Deyeshadow-palette-reviews ", "product_names": "Le Prisme Eyeshadow Quartet", "category": "Eye Makeup", "sub_category": "Eyeshadow Palette", "brand": "Givenchy Makeup", "ingredient": null, "size": "", "price": "57.00", "claims": null, "image_url": "https://www.beautypedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/952BAA02-5C53-4041-A124-656DB33317F4_31bsr9ILMBL.jpg?w=350", "expert_rating": "2", "expert_reviews": ["This soft, pressed-powder eyeshadow goes on silky-smooth with impressive color intensity, from just one swipe of the brush.", "Each compact contains four shades, including shimmer and glitter finishes; however, not all of the shades go well together and they will not flatter all skin tones. If the shade options were better coordinated and easier to work with, we would give Le Prisme Eyeshadow Quartet a higher rating, but, especially at this price, it just isn\u2019t worthy of it."], "expert_pros": null, "expert_cons": null, "jar_package": null, "animal_test": null, "user_rating": null, "product_id": 915}
